Maldini: &quot;We have needs in some roles. If you look for quality profiles they are very expensive. We have many players in sight, strong and with different characteristics. We must not be in a hurry to try to make as little mistakes as possible. Four midfielders have left and that's where we'll have to to intervene.&quot;<br />
<br />
Ricky Massara: &quot;Many profiles are linked to Milan, we are evaluating. We want to bring functional profiles only in a team that is already good. Do not worry  we know well what we need, we confront each other with the coach. This team is already competitive. We will make targeted purchases, we will be ready to seize every opportunity to strengthen the team in a functional way.&quot;
